Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.16,0:26:14.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Being just a Legion grunt
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.78,0:26:17.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I traveled wherever they needed me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.40,0:26:19.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And although the pegasi do rule the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.99,0:26:21.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The job ain't that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.56,0:26:23.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But it's not the griffons or the hippogriffs
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.11,0:26:25.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That give us much to fear
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.72,0:26:27.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When one of those giant stinking dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.05,0:26:31.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Gets a little bit too near~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.51,0:26:35.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Every tempest you may see~
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.94,0:26:39.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,None shall stay thee
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.88,0:26:43.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Knowing you are called to be
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.29,0:26:49.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Brave enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.84,0:26:51.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No matter what the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.53,0:26:53.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Forged so tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.41,0:26:55.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If it tries to kill you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.69,0:26:58.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Show your stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.31,0:26:59.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause it's them who won't be
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.85,0:27:03.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Brave enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.71,0:27:13.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then on such a mission
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.91,0:27:15.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We did have to get
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.26,0:27:16.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Across the dragon lands
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.88,0:27:18.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When we saw two of them large enough
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.83,0:27:20.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To wrap us in a single hand
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.08,0:27:22.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Many of our comrades were ensnared
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.14,0:27:25.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And taken back into their cave
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.20,0:27:26.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I could not just leave them like that
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.92,0:27:30.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There must be a way that we can save~!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.88,0:27:34.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Like feathers in a wing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.41,0:27:38.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We'd be nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.35,0:27:42.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And as one be ascending~
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.76,0:27:49.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Brave enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.28,0:27:50.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Out from the cave I led them
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.92,0:27:53.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Forged so tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.85,0:27:54.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As they tried to roast me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.12,0:27:57.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Show your stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.86,0:27:59.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With the shield I could be
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.33,0:28:03.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Brave enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.76,0:29:07.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As the storm was gathering
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.26,0:29:11.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Full of lightning
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.24,0:29:15.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You'll not be cowering
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.71,0:29:24.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Brave enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.19,0:29:25.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Somehow we really made it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.88,0:29:28.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Forged so tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.88,0:29:29.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Like the shield we all could
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.04,0:29:32.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Show your stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.81,0:29:34.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Play the role we all should
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.24,0:29:38.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Brave enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.47,0:29:40.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You've got guts
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.95,0:29:42.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To pull this all together
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.64,0:29:44.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.49,0:29:46.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yes I'm gonna join you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.80,0:29:49.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They'd be~ nuts
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.46,0:29:50.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If they think they could beat
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.00,0:29:55.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All of us!